# Funkcja do "wyciągania" predykcji z outputu z softmaxa

def p(x):
    t = x.argmax()
    out = np.zeros_like(x)
    out[t] = 1
    return out

np.random.seed(0)
n = Net(optimizer = SGD(learning_rate=0.001), loss = 'cross-entropy')
n.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(2, 5, SigmoidFunction(), RandomNormalInitializer()))
n.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(5, 5, SigmoidFunction(), RandomNormalInitializer()))
n.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(5, 2, SoftmaxAsLastLayerWithCrossEntropy(), RandomNormalInitializer()))
n.train(X, Y, X1, Y1, n_epochs=500, eval_frequency=100)
